public abstract class CommandExpression
extends AbstractExpression
A CommandExpression is an expression formed by a command name and arguments for the command. An object of this class corresponds to an invocation of the command. The name of the command can be set in plugin.xml or in this class.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
